However, 5 Gt would still have to be deducted from this balance in order to stabilise the climate increase by 2 degrees Celsius from today until 2020, in order to prevent it from becoming out of control.
In the white light bulbs 95% of the energy escapes in the form of heat, and the remaining 5% produce the light.
